Documentation

This API allows for access to data from Shamiri institute field studies from 2018 to 2020. The data were collected as part of our ongoing efforts to research and develop cost-effective and scalable interventions for at-risk youths in low-income countries. There are six different datasets available:

  • 2018 wellbeing cross-sectional survey: This contains data
